<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>入力フォームテスト文字列ツール</title>
<style>
  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; background: #f0f2f5; color: #333; }
  header { background: #2c3e50; color: #fff; padding: 16px 24px; }
  header h1 { font-size: 18px; margin-bottom: 2px; }
  header p { font-size: 12px; color: #aaa; }
  .container { max-width: 1000px; margin: 24px auto; padding: 0 16px; }
  .step-label { font-size: 12px; font-weight: bold; color: #3498db; margin-bottom: 8px; letter-spacing: 1px; }
  .field-grid { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 24px; }
  .field-btn { padding: 12px 18px; border: 2px solid #ddd; background: #fff; border-radius: 8px; cursor: pointer; font-size: 14px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 4px; min-width: 100px; transition: all 0.15s; }
  .field-btn:hover { border-color: #3498db; }
  .field-btn.active { border-color: #3498db; background: #ebf5fb; }
  .field-btn .icon { font-size: 22px; }
  .field-btn .name { font-size: 12px; color: #555; }
  .cat-tabs { display: flex; gap: 6px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .cat-tab { padding: 6px 14px; border: 1px solid #ddd; background: #fff; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 12px; cursor: pointer; }
  .cat-tab:hover { border-color: #3498db; color: #3498db; }
  .cat-tab.active { background: #3498db; color: #fff; border-color: #3498db; }
  .string-list { background: #fff; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 1px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); overflow: hidden; }
  .string-item { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; padding: 10px 16px; border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0; }
  .string-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .string-item:hover { background: #f9f9f9; }
  .cat-badge { font-size: 10px; padding: 2px 7px; border-radius: 10px; white-space: nowrap; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .badge-boundary { background: #d5f5e3; color: #1e8449; }
  .badge-special  { background: #fdebd0; color: #935116; }
  .badge-sql      { background: #f9ebea; color: #922b21; }
  .badge-xss      { background: #f9ebea; color: #922b21; }
  .badge-japanese { background: #d6eaf8; color: #1a5276; }
  .badge-emoji    { background: #fef9e7; color: #7d6608; }
  .badge-unicode  { background: #e8daef; color: #6c3483; }
  .string-meta { flex: 1; min-width: 0; }
  .string-label { font-size: 13px; font-weight: bold; color: #2c3e50; }
  .string-value { font-family: 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 12px; background: #f4f6f8; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0; border-radius: 3px; padding: 3px 7px; word-break: break-all; color: #444; margin: 3px 0; white-space: pre-wrap; }
  .string-desc { font-size: 11px; color: #888; }
  .copy-btn { padding: 5px 14px; border: 1px solid #3498db; background: #fff; color: #3498db; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 12px; cursor: pointer; white-space: nowrap; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .copy-btn:hover { background: #3498db; color: #fff; }
  .copy-btn.copied { background: #27ae60; border-color: #27ae60; color: #fff; }
  .empty { text-align: center; color: #aaa; padding: 40px; }
  .result-bar { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .result-count { font-size: 13px; color: #666; }
  .step-block { margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .divider { border: none; border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0; margin: 20px 0; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<header>
  <h1>⌨️ 入力フォームテスト文字列ツール</h1>
  <p>テストしたいフィールドを選んで、文字列をコピーして使ってください</p>
</header>
<div class="container">
  <div class="step-block">
    <div class="step-label">STEP 1 ― テストしたいフィールドを選ぶ</div>
    <div class="field-grid" id="fieldGrid"></div>
  </div>
  <hr class="divider">
  <div class="step-block" id="step2" style="display:none">
    <div class="step-label">STEP 2 ― 境界値の条件を入力する（任意）</div>
    <div style="background:#fff;border-radius:8px;padding:16px 20px;margin-bottom:16px;box-shadow:0 1px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">
      <div style="font-size:13px;color:#555;margin-bottom:10px">入力すると、境界値付近の文字列を自動生成します</div>
      <div style="display:flex;gap:16px;flex-wrap:wrap;align-items:flex-end">
        <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:4px">
          <label style="font-size:12px;color:#555">最小文字数</label>
          <div style="display:flex;gap:6px;align-items:center">
            <input type="number" id="minLen" min="0" placeholder="例: 8" style="width:90px;padding:7px 10px;border:1px solid #ccc;border-radius:5px;font-size:14px">
            <select id="minType" style="padding:7px 8px;border:1px solid #ccc;border-radius:5px;font-size:13px">
              <option value="half">半角</option>
              <option value="full">全角</option>
            </select>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:4px">
          <label style="font-size:12px;color:#555">最大文字数</label>
          <div style="display:flex;gap:6px;align-items:center">
            <input type="number" id="maxLen" min="1" placeholder="例: 100" style="width:90px;padding:7px 10px;border:1px solid #ccc;border-radius:5px;font-size:14px">
            <select id="maxType" style="padding:7px 8px;border:1px solid #ccc;border-radius:5px;font-size:13px">
              <option value="half">半角</option>
              <option value="full">全角</option>
            </select>
          </div>
        </div>
        <button onclick="applyBoundary()" style="padding:7px 18px;background:#3498db;color:#fff;border:none;border-radius:5px;font-size:13px;cursor:pointer;font-weight:bold">生成</button>
        <button onclick="clearBoundary()" style="padding:7px 14px;background:#fff;color:#888;border:1px solid #ccc;border-radius:5px;font-size:13px;cursor:pointer">クリア</button>
      </div>
      <div id="boundaryPreview" style="margin-top:12px"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="step-label">STEP 3 ― カテゴリで絞り込む（任意）</div>
    <div class="cat-tabs" id="catTabs"></div>
    <div class="result-bar">
      <span class="result-count" id="resultCount"></span>
    </div>
    <div class="string-list" id="stringList"></div>
  </div>
</div>
